title: ‘The Great British Baking Show’ Quarterfinal: “Pastry Week” | Everything Is Cake
description:
Kate is again joined this week by Rob Mahoney to dive into a messy, chaotic, and somewhat disappointing pastry-focused Quarterfinal, including a puff pastry signature, spring roll technical, and fairy-tale showstopper.
Host: Kate Halliwell
Guest: Rob Mahoney
Producer: Sasha Ashall
